      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience the thrill of owning a true automotive masterpiece! This vehicle is in breathtaking, mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Every surface is flawless, and it has been preserved with the utmost care, making it a perfect find for the most discerning collector. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a pristine example of automotive excellence!",
