    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with all service records available. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot, offering a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in like-new condition.",
      "price": 49500.0,
